    },
    "Homebrew or MacPorts is detected, but the package directory cannot be read due to sandbox restrictions.\n\nPlease go to 'System Settings → Privacy & Security → Full Disk Access', add 'Architecture Detector' to the list, and click 'Rescan'." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "检测到已安装 Homebrew 或 MacPorts，但由于沙盒限制无法读取软件包目录。\n\n请前往「系统设置 → 隐私与安全性 → 完全磁盘访问权限」，将“架构检测器”添加到列表，然后点击「重新扫描」。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hant" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "偵測到已安裝 Homebrew 或 MacPorts，但由於沙盒限制無法讀取軟體包目錄。\n\n請前往「系統設定 → 隱私權與安全性 → 完全磁碟存取權限」，將「架構檢測器」加入列表，然後點擊「重新掃描」。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
